/I-Atto-Zitti-Zitti-Coro-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="I Atto, Zitti Zitti (Coro)" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Zitti-Zitti-Coro-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Zitti-Zitti-Coro-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Zitti-Zitti-Coro-270x180.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="I Atto, Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-270x180.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-3-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="I Atto, Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna 3" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-3-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-3-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-3-270x180.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-2-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="I Atto, Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna 2" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/I-Atto-Rigoletto-Gilda-Giovanna-2-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uplo